OL,4,Ctwo-child benefit cap
OL,6,FThe Commons Speaker has selected an
OL,7,FSNP amendment to the King's Speech
OL,8,Fcalling for the cap to be axed, and
OL,9,Fleft-wing Labour MPs are expected to
OL,10,Fweigh in further to a debate.
OL,12,FMPs will vote on the proposed change
OL,13,Fon Tuesday evening. While the
OL,14,Fgovernment are not expected to lose
OL,15,Fthe vote due to their large majority,
OL,16,Fit will be the first test to see how
OL,17,Fmany backbench Labour MP's rebel.
