OL,6,FThe SNP amendment is understood to
OL,7,Fhave the support of former Labour
OL,8,Fleader and now Independent MP Jeremy
OL,9,FCorbyn, some other left-wing Labour
OL,10,Fbackbenchers, and Green and Plaid
OL,11,FCymru MPs.
OL,13,FThe cap was introduced by then-
OL,14,FConservative chancellor George Osborne
OL,15,Fin 2015.
