OL,6,FRebecca Claydon is a mother of five,
OL,7,Fand says the cap "couldn't have come
OL,8,Fat a worse time" for her family when
OL,9,Fit was introduced.
OL,11,FOne of her children was in hospital
OL,12,Fwith a brain tumour at the time, and
OL,13,Fthe family also lost their house
OL,14,Fbecause of rising living costs.
OL,16,F"Whilst I was trying to support my
OL,17,Fson, I also had the stress of finding
OL,18,Fsomewhere else to live", Rebecca told
OL,19,FITV News.
