OL,6,FShe said the cap has a huge impact on
OL,7,Ftheir family: "The kids have to go
OL,8,Fwithout a lot of the basic things. I
OL,9,Fthink the kids are suffering more than
OL,10,Fthe adults to be honest, even though
OL,11,Fthe bills are addressed to us."
OL,13,FJoe Lane, Head of Policy and Research
OL,14,Fand Action for Children told ITV News
OL,15,Flifting the cap could also "lift
OL,16,Fhundreds of thousands of children out
OL,17,Fof poverty overnight."
