OL,6,F"It is the bare minimum required to
OL,7,Ftackle child poverty ` and to begin to
OL,8,Fdeliver the change that people in
OL,9,FScotland were promised."
OL,11,FLabour's former shadow chancellor John
OL,12,FMcDonnell said he would vote for the
OL,13,FSNP change.
OL,15,FIn a video posted to X, he said: "37
OL,16,FLabour MPs like me put forward our own
OL,17,Famendment to scrap the two-child
OL,18,Flimit, but that won't be called. So
OL,19,Fthe only opportunity we'll have to
OL,20,Fvote on the two-child limit will be on
OL,21,Fan SNP motion.
