OL,6,FPhillipson said the possible scrapping
OL,7,Fof the limit would be looked at by a
OL,8,Fnew taskforce she is leading with Work
OL,9,Fand Pensions Secretary Liz Kendall as
OL,10,Fpart of a review of potential policies
OL,11,Fto reduce child poverty.
OL,13,FIn a speech at the Farnborough
OL,14,FInternational Airshow, Starmer was
OL,15,Fasked about the pressure to scrap the
OL,16,Ftwo-child limit, saying "it's good
OL,17,Fwe're having a debate about it."
OL,19,FThe PM said "I'm not surprised there's
OL,20,Fa real passion about this in the
OL,21,FLabour Party."
